{
  "name": "zagn8n Telegram Marketing Workflow",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## zagn8n Telegram-first workflow\n\nThis is the simplified version.\n\nFlow:\n1. You send a Telegram message like `daily`, `approve`, or `edit: ...`\n2. The workflow uses one control sheet only\n3. `daily` creates one draft from ZagChain performance data\n4. `approve` marks the latest draft approved and creates a Canva social-post design automatically\n5. `edit: ...` rewrites the latest draft and sends it back to Telegram\n\nRequired sheet name:\n- `zagn8n_marketing_control`\n\nRequired columns:\n- created_at\n- chat_id\n- trigger_word\n- performance_date\n- performance_summary\n- draft_text\n- approval_status\n- edit_request\n- version\n- canva_status\n- canva_design_id\n- canva_design_link\n- last_action\n\nCanva note:\n- this workflow creates a simple 1080x1080 Canva design automatically after approval\n- if you later want the draft text placed into a branded template automatically, switch the Canva step to Autofill with a Canva brand template",
        "width": 720,
        "height": 360
      },
      "id": "c8d83f50-b0d3-40e7-99e6-6e61224c98b8",
      "name": "Setup Notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1240,
        -320
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "updates": [
          "message"
        ],
        "additionalFields": {}
      },
      "id": "9c98720c-7208-40c7-ab5d-6656f9336158",
      "name": "Telegram Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.telegramTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        -1140,
        140
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const message = $json.message || {};\nconst chatId = String(message.chat?.id || '');\nconst text = String(message.text || '').trim();\nconst lower = text.toLowerCase();\n\nlet command = 'unknown';\nlet editRequest = '';\n\nif (lower === 'daily') {\n  command = 'daily';\n} else if (lower === 'approve') {\n  command = 'approve';\n} else if (lower.startsWith('edit:')) {\n  command = 'edit';\n  editRequest = text.slice(5).trim();\n}\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    chat_id: chatId,\n    telegram_text: text,\n    command,\n    edit_request: editRequest,\n    received_at: new Date().toISOString()\n  }\n}];"
      },
